<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab><expan>L<ex>ieben</ex></expan>
<expan>fr<ex>eunde</ex></expan>, wir tun <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>weish<ex>eit</ex></expan> in <expan>gut<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>frewntsch<ex>aft</ex></expan>
<expan>zu wiss<ex>en</ex></expan>, daz uns auf disz zeit von
              <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>m</expan> lieben <expan>b<ex>urger</ex></expan> und ratgesellen
                <expan>Pet<ex>er</ex>n</expan>
<expan>Volkm<ex>er</ex></expan>, der <expan>uns<ex>er</ex>s</expan> zewgs und volks gen
            Beheim <expan>hawbtma<ex>n</ex></expan> ist, brief und <expan>botsch<ex>aft</ex></expan>
            ist <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan>, der uns <expan>v<ex>er</ex>schreibt</expan>, daz <app>
<note><q type="date"><expan>am<ex>m</ex></expan>
<expan>nehstv<ex>er</ex>gang<ex>en</ex></expan> pfincztag</q>02.10.1421</note>
</app> ein <expan>gancz<ex>er</ex></expan> aufpruch des hers in Beheim vor der stat Sacz
                <expan>geschehe<ex>n</ex></expan> ist, und daz <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> gnedig
                <expan>h<ex>er</ex>ren</expan> die <expan>erczbisch<ex>of</ex></expan> von Tryr und
            von Cöln und <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan> und etlich <expan>and<ex>er</ex></expan> volk
                <expan>am<ex>m</ex></expan>
<app>
<note><q type="date"><expan>nehstvergang<ex>en</ex></expan> sunntag zu nacht</q>05.10.1421</note>
</app> des wegs <expan>h<ex>er</ex>heim</expan> zu ziehen bis <add>zum</add> Radisfurt
            enhalb Eger <expan>kome<ex>n</ex></expan> seyn; so ziehe <expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>gnedig<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>h<ex>er</ex>re</expan> der pfallnczgraf die <expan>and<ex>er</ex>n</expan> strass
            für Tachaw <expan>h<ex>er</ex>awsz</expan> heymwarts. Denn wo wir
              <expan>ewr<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>ersamk<ex>eit</ex></expan> lieb <expan>od<ex>er</ex></expan> dienst etc.
                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan> ut <expan>s<ex>upra</ex></expan>.</ab>
</div>
